

HIMALA

   root words: hing + balà
   hi·ma·lâ
   miracle

   mga himalâ
   miracles

   Ito ay himalâ.
   = Himala ito.
   This is a miracle.

   May himalang naganap.
   There was a miracle that happened.

   The Spanish-derived equivalent word that is also widely used, though
   with a slight difference in nuance, is [66]milagro.

MGA KAHULUGAN SA TAGALOG

